"Very basic support for `Relay <https://github.com/facebook/relay>`_ is "
"included."
msgstr ""

#: ../../relay.rst:7
msgid ""
"**Note**: Relay refers here to \"Relay Classic\", there is no support for"
" \"Relay Modern\"."
